title: In-Person Captain Meeting
location: Tempe Beach Park, 80 W Rio Salado, Tempe (Ballfield)
event_notes:
Good morning!

Three weeks to race day! Thank you for all your hard work. If I have not had a chance to officially meet or email with you, feel free to reach out. There are a lot of new names and faces and I am trying to respond as quickly as possible. I am available for questions or concerns and if I don't have the answer, I will find it. I appreciate the patience!

We will have a mandatory in-person meeting on Wednesday, 11/13 @ 5:30. At this meeting you will get a chance to meet with the staff about your area and get your captain's gear. Dinner will be served. Parking is free with the attached parking pass.

I hope to see you there - if you absolutely cannot make it, email me directly (no need to respond to all) or call/text: 602 620-4208 and we can make arrangements for info/gear.

Thank you- you are truly appreciated.
Jolie
